name: Genome-Peptide-Structure
tagline: A workshop to discuss interconnection of PDB, Kaviar, PeptideAtlas, and TPP, for BD Spokes Planning Grant
body:
A two-day workshop at the Institute for Systems Biology in Seattle, Washington, for collaborators and other researchers working toward the interconnection of genomic, proteomic, and protein structure data.

The workshop will take place sometime during the first two weeks of January, 2017.

Contact Eric Deutsch, edeutsch@systemsbiology.org, if you are interested in being invited to the meeting.
